member (section 2.2.4.1) of the <i>WkstaInfo</i> parameter into elements of the
ADM, as follows:</p><ul><li><p><span><span> 
</span></span><b>wki1046_dormant_file_limit</b> stored in <b>DormantFileLimit</b>.</p>
